    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1934-04-30T12:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1934-04-30T12:00:00-05:00" n="440"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d440">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">721.23/2248: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Switzerland</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wilson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Geneva</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-04-30T18:00:00+01:00"
                            >April 30, 1934—6 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received April 30—1:25 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>238. My 236, April 26, noon.</p>
                <list>
                    <label>1.</label>
                    <item>Circular from Secretariat today’s date reports that the Brazilian
                        representative has informed the Advisory Committee on Leticia that Mello
                        Franco in accord with the Colombian and Peruvian delegations has suggested
                        that the meeting of the Committee be adjourned since there are grounds to
                        hope that the negotiations at Rio will bring about an agreement between the
                        two Governments before May 10th.</item>
                    <label>2.</label>
                    <item>The meeting of the Committee is therefore postponed until May 15th.</item>
                </list>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
